review_text:
“From our initial video interview onwards, my interactions with Bridge have always been friendly, professional and helpful.<br>
They went to the effort to find out exactly what my requirements were and, as a result, was able to match me with a highly suitable employer. <br>
It&#039;s such a good match, that I&#039;m currently in negotiations to extend my contract by another year.<br>
Throughout the application process, Scarlett always answered my queries, no matter how minor. <br>
And when she didn&#039;t immediately know the answer, she did her best to quickly find out and get back to me.&#034; <br>
&#034;This professionalism continued after my arrival in Korea when many agents consider their job done and sever contact with teachers they&#039;ve placed. <br>
Bridge is still available to answer any questions I have, or just to share a friendly chat.<br>
I heartily recommend anyone considering seeking employment in Korea contact Bridge and take the first step in finding the perfect placement.&#034;<br>









